### Get all images
GET http://localhost:3000/api/images

### Get one image by ID (valid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/images/69a36b75607e5fe9961ae496

### Get one image by ID (non-existent but valid ObjectId format)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/images/69a36b75607e5fe9961ae4ff

### Get one image by ID (invalid ObjectId format — triggers 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/images/not-a-valid-id

### Rename image (valid request)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/images/69a36b75607e5fe9961ae496
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "A beautiful blue merle" }

### Rename image — bad request (missing name field)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/images/69a36b75607e5fe9961ae496
Content-Type: application/json

{ "title": "wrong field" }

### Rename image — image not found (valid ObjectId but doesn't exist)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/images/69a36b75607e5fe9961ae4ff
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "New name" }

### Rename image — content too large (name exceeds 100 characters)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/images/69a36b75607e5fe9961ae496
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "This name is intentionally made to be way too long so that it exceeds the one hundred character limit that has been set on the server" }
